    <title>20210606 속초는 어때?</title>
    <link>https://qodot.github.io/obsidian-public/2021/20210606-%E1%84%89%E1%85%A9%E1%86%A8%E1%84%8E%E1%85%A9%E1%84%82%E1%85%B3%E1%86%AB-%E1%84%8B%E1%85%A5%E1%84%84%E1%85%A2</link>
